parameters:
\n<Ameria>"Why, why! No! Why would you say such a thing today of all
days!?"

\n<Lyric>"You're so noisy, it's because it's today.--Ah, stop
clinging to me! Get off, idiot!"
\n<Roselitte>"...What in the world is going on, it's so noisy."

\n<Ameria>"She's going to leave me all alone and go somewhere! She
doesn't care about me anymore!"
\n<Roselitte>"Huh?... Succubus, where do you plan to go?"

\n<Lyric>"I'm not going anywhere... I just said I want to sleep
alone."

\n<Lyric>"This girl, even at her age, can't sleep alone at night.
She's afraid of the dark~ and clings to me all night long."

\n<Roselitte>"Ahh... I see. That's why you brought a large amount of
firewood."
\n<Ameria>"Uhh... but... ghosts come out at night..."

\n<Lyric>"They don't, you idiot.... Seriously, there's a demon right
in front of you. If you're going to be scared, be scared of
me."

\n<Lyric>"There's a knight here tonight. Sometimes I want to sleep
peacefully on my own, too."
\n<Lyric>"...That's the situation. I'm leaving Ameria's care to you."

\n<Lyric>"Nfufu. I don't want you sneaking up on me while I'm asleep.
I'll relax in a place a little further away."
\n<Ameria>"Um... Roselitte-san, I have a favor to ask..."
\n<Roselitte>"...It's okay to sleep together if that's what you want."
\n<Ameria>"Really? Wow, thank you! I like you more than Lyric!"
